    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Game About Robots!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to be a Scrapper, or are you just another piece of JUNK?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle with your friends, random opponents, or an AI trainer to unlock new robots, abilities, and customizations. JUNK! is a fast paced, arena 1v1 PVP brawler.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EARLY ACCESS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >JUNK! is being built by a very small team of designers and developers with a roadmap that will extend over the next few years. The current plan is to provide monthly balance updates, quarterly content updates (Robots, Arenas, Abilities, Cosmetics), and patches/bug fixes as necessary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178300/extras/8d3ebeb3e05d5d112ca8ce527bfb5e78.avif?t=1757644340\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178300/extras_big/8d3ebeb3e05d5d112ca8ce527bfb5e78.avif?t=1757644340 width=800 height=264 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHOOSE YOUR ROBOT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each robot has unique aspects like speed, armor, and attack power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178300/extras/5be7829a2abf50325e81c2a478937da0.avif?t=1757644340\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178300/extras_big/5be7829a2abf50325e81c2a478937da0.avif?t=1757644340 width=800 height=178 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Moth: Ultra-light and ultra-fast!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hopper: Nimble and quick, you'll never know what hit you!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tusk: Massive and powerful!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178300/extras/d9d4b733a4f3db3096f6f0fc80cf855c.avif?t=1757644340\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178300/extras_big/d9d4b733a4f3db3096f6f0fc80cf855c.avif?t=1757644340 width=800 height=264 /></span><strong></strong><br><br><strong>UNIQUE ABILITIES AND COSMETICS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find an edge by using special abilities and stand out with a new coat of paint!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178300/extras/bcfdfe52de04930d144b84754f673be6.avif?t=1757644340\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178300/extras_big/bcfdfe52de04930d144b84754f673be6.avif?t=1757644340 width=800 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178300/extras/4659489e2def921245c23b25372f9aed.avif?t=1757644340\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178300/extras_big/4659489e2def921245c23b25372f9aed.avif?t=1757644340 width=800 height=264 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PVP BATTLE ARENAS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your metal in each of the Battle Arenas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178300/extras/32f09f4a2e55f7cbcd98951ce58f28a8.avif?t=1757644340\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178300/extras_big/32f09f4a2e55f7cbcd98951ce58f28a8.avif?t=1757644340 width=800 height=266 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Dome: Small and open, the Dome is a balanced arena, letting new Scrappers learn how to wreck their opponents.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Silo: Do you have what it takes to compete in this medium size arena, with unique geometry and powerups?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Lair: Only the most skilled Scrappers can take on the challenges of this massive arena!</p></li></ul>",
